## Make Targets (grouped by section)

### Check Bastion Configs
| Target | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `make check-env` | Verify all required env vars + test logins |
| `make add-docker-repo` | Trust IMAGE_REGISTRY on both clusters |

### Build Artifacts
| Target | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `make upload-acm-chart` | Push RHACM chart to OCI (admin token) |
| `make upload-sovereign-namespaces-chart` | Push namespace chart to OCI |
| `make upload-rhbk-chart` | Push Keycloak operator+instance chart to OCI |
| `make upload-rhbk-config-chart` | Push Keycloak config chart to OCI |
| `make upload-acs-chart` | Push ACS chart to OCI |
| `make upload-vault-chart` | Push Vault chart to OCI |
| `make upload-aap-chart` | Push AAP chart to OCI |
| `make upload-odf-chart` | Push ODF chart to OCI |
| `make upload-quay-chart` | Push Quay chart to OCI |
| `make upload-crunchy-postgres-chart` | Push Crunchy Postgres for Kubernetes chart to OCI |
| `make upload-gitea-chart` | Push Gitea chart to OCI |
| `make ansible-runner` | Build + push ansible-runner image |

### Bootstrap Cluster
| Target | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `make init-central-argo` | Deploy init chart → ApplicationSet → ArgoCD takes over |

## Key rules for agents working in each directory

- `helm/charts/*` — after any change: `helm lint`, bump `Chart.yaml` version, re-run `make upload-*`.
- `helm/central` — run `helm lint` after every change; update `values.yaml` when OCI chart is bumped.
- `helm/init` — bootstrap entry-point; changes affect both clusters; test with `helm template`.
- `make/*.mk` — each target in its own file; keep root Makefile as a thin importer.
- `ansible/roles/*` — all task logic; playbooks only call roles. Test with `ansible-playbook` locally before packaging.
- `ansible/project/*` — playbooks that ONLY call roles from `ansible/roles/`.
- `architecture/docs/` — keep diagrams small, one concept per file.
- `architecture/hardeningcheck/` — update after any security-impacting change.
